{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "padelito-api-v1-full",
		"name": "Padelito - API v1 (Onboarding, Auth, Player, Matches)",
		"description": "Routes `api/v1` pour Onboarding, Auth, Player et Matches.\n\n- **Sanctum** : la collection utilise `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` par défaut.\n- **Public (`noauth`)** : register, login, reset-password, reset-password/confirm.\n- Après **Register** ou **Login**, copie la valeur `token` de la réponse JSON dans la variable de collection `token`.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8001"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "public_username",
			"value": "johndoe"
		},
		{
			"key": "match_id",
			"value": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001"
		},
		{
			"key": "invitation_id",
			"value": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002"
		},
		{
			"key": "invitee_player_id",
			"value": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Onboarding",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register player",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Jean Dupont\",\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Str0ng!PassWord\"\n}\n",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/register",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"v1",
								"register"
							]
						},
						"description": "Crée un utilisateur (`RegisterRequest` : `name`, `email` unique, `password`). Règles mot de passe : ≥12 caractères, au moins une majuscule, une minuscule, un chiffre et un caractère spécial parmi ceux acceptés par `Password` (domaine Auth). Réponse 201 avec `token` et `data.user`."
					}
				}
			]
		},
